'''Raouf J. Jacob''' (wavutse 1988 muri [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone, [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Iburengerazuba), ni umukinnyi wa firime, producer akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime]].  Jacob azwi cyane kubera filime nyinshi yatsindiye ibihembo muri  filime za ''[[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone:'' ''A Culture of Silence''.  Ni n'Umuyobozi Nshingwabikorwa & Rurema akaba n'uwashinze sitidiyo / filime za Worldwide Cinema Frames LLC hamwe na Global Cinema Film Festival ya Boston (GCFF) yashinze mu 2006. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2005, yakoze filime CRY'','' ''America'', yakoze ubushakashatsi ku byago bibabaje no gukurikira <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hurricane_Katrina" rel="mw:ExtLink" title="Hurricane Katrina" class="cx-link" data-linkid="54">Hurricane Katrina</a> ndetse na  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2003_invasion_of_Iraq" rel="mw:ExtLink" title="2003 invasion of Iraq" class="cx-link" data-linkid="55">the American war against Iraq</a>i . Yakoze kandi urukurikirane ''a Blind World.'' . Uruhererekane rwasesenguye Umunyagitugu w’Abanazi [[Adolf Hitler]] ' Igisubizo cya nyuma cy’ikibazo cy’Abayahudi ', [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Jenoside yo mu Rwanda yo]] mu 1994, itsembabwoko rya Darfur muri Sudani, itotezwa ry’umuryango wa Baha'i muri Irani ndetse n’ingoma y’uwahoze ari intwazangabo Pablo Escobar muri [[Kolombiya]]. 

Muri 2014, Jacob yashyize ahagaragara film documentaire '':'' ''A Culture of Silence'' Yabaye umuyobozi, umwanditsi, producer, umukinnyi wa cinemateri, umwanditsi hamwe nivanga amajwi ya firime. Iyi filime yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi, harimo Filime nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya New York City 2014, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Boston 2014, ndetse n’iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Roxbury 2014. Iyi filime kandi yerekanwe ku Isoko rya Filime rya Cannes 2014 (Marché du film de Cannes), Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Afurika rya Silicon n'ibindi!  

